'''Halo lamps''' were hand-held, disc-shaped lamps that generated light around their circumference. Larger than [[Glowrod/Legends|glow rods]], halo lamps were typically installed aboard [[Starship/Legends|starships]] or vehicles.

An alternate handheld version of the halo lamp also existed. No larger than the palm of a [[Human/Legends|Human]] [[Limb/Legends|hand]], the disc shaped light glowed with a [[Color/Legends|white]] light that radiated outward in a three [[Meter/Legends|meter]] radius. The light source was cool to the touch, and could be easily attached to other objects.<ref name="Clone">''[[The Clone Wars Campaign Guide]]''</ref>

